re mana of any color to cast this spell&quot; and &quot;When you cast this spell, return a creature named <mark>Ominous</mark> Traveler you control to its owner&#x27;s hand.&quot;"}, {"card": "Tarkir Omenpath", "set": "UNK", "html": "{T}: Add {C}.\n{T}: Add one mana of any color. Spend this mana only to cast <mark>Omen</mark> spells.\n{1}, {T}: Add one mana of any color."}, {"card": "Soulcipher Board // Cipherbound Spirit", "set": "INR", "html": "This artifact enters with three <mark>omen</mark> counters on it."}, {"card": "Dragonsoul Prodigy", "set": "YTDM", "html": "Whenever you cast your first <mark>Omen</mark> spell each turn, conjure a duplicate of that card onto the battlefield. It gains haste. At the beginning of the next end step, shuffle it into its owner&#x27;s library."}, {"card": "A-Ominous Parcel", "set": "SNC", "html": "{1}, {T}, Sacrifice <mark>Ominous</mark> Parcel: Search your library for a basic land card, reveal it, put it into your hand, then shuffle.\n{5}, {T}, Sacrifice <mark>Ominous</mark> Parcel: It deals 4 damage to target creature."}, {"card": "Celestial Convergence", "set": "PCY", "html": "This enchantment enters with seven <mark>omen</mark> counters on it."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/9/29306305-cb71-4fef-bf86-f5deb4e7e561.jpg?1782705504", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/2/9/29306305-cb71-4fef-bf86-f5deb4e7e561.jpg?1782705504", "card": "Strategic Planning"}}